description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Potomac, which features a party thrown by Karen complete with a video invite. Danny also interviews Heather Rae Young from Selling Sunset on Netflix. They discuss how real the show is, paparazzi, her time with Playboy, and lots more!


Heather Rae Young Interview: 25:10ish

Watch the Heather Rae Young interview on YouTube: YouTube.com/DannyPellegrino1
